# 🍪 Golden Crumb Bakery - Commit Message Template
# 
# Format: <type>(<scope>): <description>
#
# Types:
# ✨ feat:     New feature
# 🐛 fix:      Bug fix
# 📚 docs:     Documentation changes
# 🎨 style:    Code style changes (formatting, etc.)
# ♻️  refactor: Code refactoring
# 🚀 perf:     Performance improvements
# ✅ test:     Adding or updating tests
# 🔧 chore:    Maintenance tasks
# 🍪 content:  Cookie/bakery content updates
#
# Examples:
# ✨ feat(cookies): add new snickerdoodle recipe
# 🐛 fix(images): resolve broken cookie image paths
# 🎨 style(css): improve responsive design for mobile
# 🍪 content(menu): update seasonal cookie prices
#
# Remember to:
# - Use present tense ("add" not "added")
# - Keep first line under 50 characters
# - Include detailed description if needed below
#
# This template helps create consistent, meaningful commit messages
# for the Golden Crumb Bakery website project.